N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 18 ยง 344.1 - Purpose

State Regulations

This Part establishes procedures for income withholding
of child support or combined child and spousal support for persons who are not
in receipt of title IV-D child support services from a social services
district. Notes
